								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>206 folios (+ 2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and 3 at the end). </p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>19 quires of 10 leaves each, 1 quire (no. 20) of 8 leaves, and 1 quire (no. 21) of 7 leaves - defective, plus a detached leaf at the end. </p>
									<p>Signed with Hebrew letters at the beginning and at the end of quires. </p>
