						<additions>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="author">Se'adyah ben Shelomoh</name>: probably a compiler of this manuscript: inscribed, folio 61r. The Judeo-Arabic sentence at the end of Deuteronomy, folio 189v, implies that the author had employed a copyist. </p>
